Apply Tags to Embossed cards to allow flexibility for Ascendancy nodes like: 
Searing Insight -   Playing Fire or Chaos cards drains 2% HP, granting +4% damage for 1 turn (stacks 5x).
(Heavy Strike Embossed with "Ignition" gives Heavy Strike "Fire" Tag)
(Arcane Bolt Embossed with "Ritualistic Intent" gives Arcane Bolt "Chaos" Tag)